spells.description:

name: Cyrce's Circlet
description: Sea dogs and tale spinners tell stories of a mythical siren that could lure even the stubbornest sailors to a watery grave.

spells.description: Equip: Your damaging abilities have a very high chance to charge the magnet, up to 30 times.

Use: Reverse the magnet's polarity to violently recycle buried garbage, dealing 103,923 Plague damage to your target per charge. Lingering virulence deals 10% of the damage dealt to 5 nearby enemies over 6 sec. (20 Sec Cooldown)

Use: Coat the enemy in a layer of unstable slime, dealing 1.1 million Nature damage over 10 sec. If the target dies while slimed, it releases corrosive goo that deals 562,659 Nature damage, split between nearby enemies. (1 Min 30 Sec Cooldown)
